# 🎨 MULTFILM BOT - O'ZBEK TELEGRAM BOTI

Telegram orqali bolalar multfilmlarini yuborish uchun to'liq bot tizimlari bilan birga.

## 📋 Xususiyatlari

✅ Telegram botida multfilm yuborish
✅ Bepul paket (haftada 2 ta multfilm)
✅ Premium obuna (20,000 so'm/oy - cheksiz multfilm)
✅ Admin panel orqali multfilm qo'shish
✅ Foydalanuvchi statistikasi
✅ Qidirysh va filtrlash
✅ Avtomatik haftalik reset
✅ 👶 Bolalar uchun xavfsiz!

---

## 🚀 O'RNATISH (Setup)

### 1. Node.js O'RNATISH

Windows/Mac/Linux uchun:
https://nodejs.org/ dan o'rnating (LTS versiyasi tavsiya qilinadi)

### 2. Proyektni O'RNATISH

```bash
# Fayllarni yuklab oling
git clone <url>
cd multfilm-bot

# Paketlarni o'rnating
npm install
```

### 3. BOT TOKEN O'RNATISH

`bot.js` faylida token o'zlashtiring:
```javascript
const TOKEN = '8707470724:AAGAI02VK56b077kBYYNPfjs6yyAEs5JEOI';
```

@BotFather dan o'zingizning tokenni oling: https://t.me/BotFather

### 4. BOTNI ISHGA TUSHIRISH

```bash
npm start
```

Yoki development rejimida:
```bash
npm run dev
```

