Bot ma'lumotlarni JSON formatida saqlaydi:

### movies.json
```json
{
  "001": {
    "code": "001",
    "nameUz": "Multfilm nomi",
    "nameEn": "Cartoon Title",
    "desc": "Tavsif",
    "year": "2024",
    "genre": "Sarguzasht",
    "url": "https://example.com/cartoon.mp4",
    "duration": "25"
  }
}
```

### users.json
```json
{
  "123456789": {
    "chatId": "123456789",
    "username": "user",
    "plan": "free", // yoki "premium"
    "freeBudget": 2,
    "premiumExpires": "2024-12-31",
    "downloadsThisWeek": 0
  }
}
```

