## 🔧 DEPLOYMENT (Serverda O'RNATISH)

### Heroku Orqali (Bepul)

```bash
# Heroku CLI o'rnating
npm install -g heroku

# Login qiling
heroku login

# App yarating
heroku create multfilm-bot

# Environment variables o'zlashtiring
heroku config:set BOT_TOKEN=YOUR_TOKEN

# Deploy qiling
git push heroku main

# Logs ko'ring
heroku logs --tail
```

### Railway Orqali (Bepul)
1. https://railway.app ga oching
2. GitHub account bilan login qiling
3. Proyektni connect qiling
4. Deploy qiling

### VPS (Pullik, to'liq control)
1. Linux VPS sotib oling
2. Node.js o'rnating
3. Proyektni clone qiling
4. `npm start` chiqarasiz

